cat <<EOF
PodBrowser is a documentation browser for Perl. You can view the documentation
for Perl's builtin functions, its "perldoc" pages, pragmatic modules and
the default and user-installed modules.

PodBrowser is a more feature-complete version of podviewer.
EOF
